Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.32,0:00:03.26,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,I knew it. You...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.26,0:00:05.48,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,really do have an interesting Sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.03,0:00:07.64,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.64,0:00:09.14,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,No, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.96,0:00:12.73,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Who the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.04,0:00:20.03,Default,Kokona and Shizuka,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.03,0:00:22.20,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,They can see you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.03,0:00:22.20,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,They can see me?!
