Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:01:59.01,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an3\pos(1754.799,926.799)\fnTimes New Roman\fs54\bord3\3c&H4B4B4C&\blur6\fad(770,770)}Once Upon a Time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.54,0:02:03.27,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,"The final show of\N{\i1}The Tale of the Bamboo Cutter{\i0}."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.27,0:02:05.88,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,"Audience brought to tears by the \Nsinging of lead actress Yae Niizuma..."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.89,0:02:09.08,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(956.307,911.538)\fnArial\fs60\c&H2B243E&\3c&HFDFFFD&\fad(1,160)}The Final Show of SIRIUS's {\i1}The Tale of the Bamboo Cutter{\i0}\NAudience brought to tears by the singing of lead actress Yae Niizuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:08.32,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,{\an8}She was so amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.32,0:02:10.95,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,{\an8}All the comments are about her, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.08,0:02:09.83,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,{\an4\fnArial\fs48\shad0\c&H2B243E&\3c&HFDFFFD&\fad(170,120)}Yae Niizuma starred in {\i1}The Tale of the Bamboo Cutter{\i0} at SIRIUS's theater in Asakusa.\NAs most readers probably know, SIRIUS is a female acting troupe put together by \Nour country's renowned World Dai Star, Shamo Yamabuki. Their performances regularly sell out,\N and while SIRIUS is gaining national attention, the one who shines the brightest among them\N is Yae Niizuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.83,0:02:11.33,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,{\an4\fnArial\fs48\shad0\c&H2B243E&\3c&HFDFFFD&\fad(120,120)}Niizuma's rendition of Princess Kaguya was delicate, and she put on a fantastic performance\Nthat made the audience feel how strong her will was at times. Her solo during the climax was \Ntruly a highlight, and the whole audience was brought to tears, overwhelmed with emotion\N from Niizuma's song overflowing with her Sense. I definitely saw her potential as a future\N Dai Star as she captivated the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:10.75,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(317.538,944.769)\fnArial\fs42\c&H2B243E&\3c&HFDFFFD&\fad(280,120)}Yae{**-chan} was amazing in {\i1}The Tale of the Bamboo Cutter{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.75,0:02:11.50,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(317.538,944.769)\fnArial\fs42\c&H2B243E&\3c&HFDFFFD&}She really was! I'm definitely catching the next show!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.50,0:02:12.25,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(317.538,944.769)\fnArial\fs42\c&H2B243E&\3c&HFDFFFD&}I cried every time I saw it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.25,0:02:13.00,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(317.538,944.769)\fnArial\fs42\c&H2B243E&\3c&HFDFFFD&}I'm a Yae{**-chan} fan after seeing {\i1}The Tale of the Bamboo Cutter{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:13.80,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(317.538,944.769)\fnArial\fs42\c&H2B243E&\3c&HFDFFFD&}Niizuma's talent stands out, even in the current acting world...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.25,0:02:17.06,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,{\an8}How is no one talking about you, Kokona?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:14.50,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(317.538,944.769)\fnArial\fs42\c&H2B243E&\3c&HFDFFFD&}I'm going to go to every production Yae{**-chan}'s in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.50,0:02:14.90,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(317.538,944.769)\fnArial\fs42\c&H2B243E&\3c&HFDFFFD&}She's cute, an amazing singer, and such a talented actress... What a prodigy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.06,0:02:17.82,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:20.99,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You poured your heart into that performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:26.77,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,So why isn't anyone saying, \N"Oh my gosh, she's amazing"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.77,0:02:30.47,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Oh! I found a comment about \Nyou, Kathrina{**-chan}! Lookie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.15,0:02:32.20,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.20,0:02:33.54,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I'll read it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:35.55,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(707.076,376.155)\fnLato\fs48\b1\bord0\c&H524F5F&}Voice call has ended
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:35.55,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(707.076,710.31)\fnLato\fs48\b1\bord0\c&H524F5F&}Voice call has ended
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:44.97,Subtitles,Theresa/Subs,0,0,0,,{\pos(955.635,867)}Great performance. I saw the stream. Good job getting\N over that hiccup. You have some wonderful costars.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:46.35,Subtitles,Kathrina,0,0,0,,...Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.47,0:02:48.48,Subtitles,Theresa/Subs,0,0,0,,Have you thanked them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:50.39,Subtitles,Kathrina/Subs,0,0,0,,...Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.66,0:02:53.96,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Man, she really is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:56.59,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey! Are you okay with that?! \NDoesn't it frustrate you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:02:55.21,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,H—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.59,0:02:57.81,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,{\an8}Er, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.00,0:02:58.31,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Hey, Ko—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.62,0:03:00.52,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Heya, are all three of you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.52,0:03:01.42,Default,Kokona; Shizuka; Kathrina,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.07,0:03:05.95,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnComic Sans MS\fs90\b1\c&HAC6AE1&\3c&HF8FFFC&}Move{\c&H74F3F3&}-in {\c&HAC6AE1&}party{\c&H74F3F3&}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.07,0:03:05.95,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnComic Sans MS\fs90\b1\bord12\c&HAC6AE1&\3c&HE0CFFB&}Move{\c&H74F3F3&\3c&HC9D7EF&}-in {\c&HAC6AE1&\3c&HE0CFFB&}party{\c&H74F3F3&\3c&HC9D7EF&}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.73,0:03:05.86,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,A move-in party?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.22,0:03:07.45,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:12.73,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,It's tradition at this dorm to throw a \Nparty after the newcomer performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.73,0:03:14.40,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,How do your schedules look today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.40,0:03:16.44,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,You're not working today, Koko{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.44,0:03:20.20,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Huh? No, I'm not... \NBut how do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:22.67,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,That means tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.67,0:03:25.43,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,We'll be throwing a move-in party
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:29.99,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,for Koko{**-chan}, Kathrin, \Nand Oshizu{**-chan} as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.55,0:03:31.56,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Yay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:33.96,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Um... I'm allowed to join, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.96,0:03:35.83,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,But of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:38.57,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Actually, you're all required to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:40.19,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:41.81,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Kathrin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.17,0:03:46.07,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,You! Will! Be! There!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.76,0:03:50.09,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,F... F-Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.09,0:03:53.06,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,I can't wait to try your cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:53.79,Default,Kathrina; Kokona; Shizuka,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.66,0:03:59.91,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,It's tradition for the newbies to each\Nmake a dish for the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.91,0:04:02.63,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,What? Even though the party's for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:04.72,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,What can I say? It's tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:05.61,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.61,0:04:06.67,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.67,0:04:10.40,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,I've never had authentic German food before!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:12.90,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Kathrina{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.57,0:04:14.90,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Let's do our best together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:19.01,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Kathrina{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.10,0:04:23.03,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,So be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.92,0:04:26.40,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Now that that's decided, let's go shopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:27.08,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.08,0:04:28.09,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Whoa there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.51,0:04:31.56,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,You're staying here, Oshizu{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.56,0:04:32.16,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:36.96,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,We're very interested in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:38.37,Default,Kokona and Shizuka,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:39.38,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Panda is, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.79,0:04:40.68,Default,Kokona and Shizuka,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:45.46,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,I sure am! I've never encountered\Nsuch a unique Sense before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:47.88,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,I'm just so curious that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:50.22,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,See? I've got dark circles under my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:53.65,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,I mean, it's honestly pretty cute \Nand makes me seem more panda-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.65,0:04:56.38,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Huh? Um, uh... sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.38,0:04:59.54,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,How do you change clothes? \NOr hop in the bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.54,0:05:02.82,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Hey, do you disappear if you \Nget too far from Koko{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:05.28,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.48,0:05:09.81,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure it'll be fine.\NAnyway, looking forward to the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.81,0:05:11.24,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Kokona!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:13.66,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Shizuka{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:16.54,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Is she going to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:18.12,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,No idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.74,0:05:23.30,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,But I'm sure Shizuka{**-chan} would enjoy\Nsome time away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:25.02,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Let's go shopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.53,0:05:27.56,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,You sure bounce back quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:33.06,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(544.731,433.262)\org(549.231,435.153)\fscx96.928\fscy83.157\frz-26.423\fry-10.893\frx-10.445\fax0.121\fnArial\fs36\b1\xbord0\ybord0\c&H9C969D&\fad(1840,1)}SIRIUS SENTO
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:33.05,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I wonder what I should make.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:36.33,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:41.15,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Is there anything you'd\Nlike to eat, Kathrina{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:42.62,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Like a favorite food?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:45.11,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:46.79,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Who exactly is Shizuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.26,0:05:50.41,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,She's Shizuka{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.44,0:05:54.42,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Okay, let me put it another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.76,0:05:57.67,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,What exactly is your Sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.26,0:05:59.74,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.96,0:06:07.35,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,A jungle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.35,0:06:11.02,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,We get all kinds of things from \Nfans after playing various roles.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:13.24,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,We got bamboo shoots this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.24,0:06:16.76,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Sassu fans are just too clever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.99,0:06:21.84,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Now, then... How much do you \Nknow about Senses, Oshizu{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:24.28,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Honestly, not much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:27.42,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,So you really don't even \Nknow much about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:29.04,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,What a curious Sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:37.36,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Senses are special traits that \Nbegan emerging when actors
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.36,0:06:39.99,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,started desiring a higher \Nlevel of expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:48.25,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,A little before the current acting scene \Nbecame known as the great age of theater,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:52.68,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,the stage was overrun with actors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.34,0:06:55.81,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,In order for actors to survive,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:58.54,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,special abilities were born\Nto help them take the spotlight
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:07:01.14,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,and shine the brightest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.53,0:07:03.65,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Those are what we call Senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:07.88,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Just like animals adapt in order to survive,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.88,0:07:10.52,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,I wonder if actors evolved, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.52,0:07:12.02,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Evolved?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.02,0:07:19.43,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Basically, we figure Senses are just \Na super-amazing form of expression
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:21.78,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,that only manifests onstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.43,0:07:25.81,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,But Oshizu{**-chan}, you're sorta... different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:31.15,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,There are actors who can awaken \Na different personality
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.15,0:07:34.14,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,within them via their Sense\N to fit certain roles.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:38.18,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,It's rare, but there are even actors\Nwho can change their appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:42.36,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, they remain \Na single actor on the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:45.90,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,It's inconceivable for another personality\Nto appear alongside you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:48.26,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,that other people can see, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:51.68,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Not to mention,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:54.96,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,you don't seem to disappear when \Nyou leave the stage or Koko{**-chan}'s side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:58.83,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,I wonder what Koko{**-chan}'s Sense really is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.48,0:08:02.68,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,What exactly are you, Oshizu{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:04.59,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.05,0:08:07.58,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,As for Shizuka{**-chan}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:11.59,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I met her during a time when I was \Nfailing one audition after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:17.83,Flashback,Hamlet (Kokona),0,0,0,,To be! Or not to be! That is the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:21.52,Flashback,Judge A,0,0,0,,You're not bad, but you lack Sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:24.18,Flashback,Judge B,0,0,0,,You don't have any Sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.18,0:08:27.28,Flashback,Judge C,0,0,0,,You need Sense that can excite the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:45.79,Flashback,Kokona,0,0,0,,Maybe I can't be a Dai Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.49,0:08:51.48,Flashback,Kokona,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:54.43,Flashback,Kokona,0,0,0,,I {\i1}can{\i0} be a Dai Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.94,0:08:57.71,Flashback,Kokona,0,0,0,,I can! I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.27,0:08:59.53,Flashback,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:05.50,Flashback,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I was watching you perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:08.31,Flashback,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I thought you did pretty well myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:10.11,Flashback,Kokona,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:13.53,Flashback,Shizuka,0,0,0,,But you need to have more \Nconfidence in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:16.86,Flashback,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You need to stand proud \Nand let them know, "I'm right here!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:18.98,Flashback,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Your performance needs that kind of passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.31,0:09:20.68,Flashback,Kokona,0,0,0,,"I'm right here"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:21.36,Flashback,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.36,0:09:21.75,Flashback,Kokona,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:27.87,Flashback,Shizuka (Hamlet),0,0,0,,To be or not to be—that is the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:30.85,Flashback,Kokona,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't go doing that right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.85,0:09:32.93,Flashback,Shizuka (Hamlet),0,0,0,,Whether 'tis nobler...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:33.62,Flashback,Kokona,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.56,0:09:37.79,Flashback,Shizuka (Hamlet),0,0,0,,...in the mind to suffer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:41.41,Flashback,Shizuka (Hamlet),0,0,0,,The slings and arrows \Nof outrageous fortune,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:44.88,Flashback,Shizuka (Hamlet),0,0,0,,Or to take arms against a sea of troubles
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:48.11,Flashback,Shizuka (Hamlet),0,0,0,,And, by opposing, end them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:51.19,Flashback,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:53.49,Flashback,Kokona,0,0,0,,Wow! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:56.05,Flashback,Kokona,0,0,0,,So that's how I should've \Nperformed that scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:09:58.40,Flashback,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You can do it too, Kokona.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.12,0:10:00.63,Flashback,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I'm Shizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:05.05,Flashback,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I'll make you shine brighter\Nthan anyone as an actor...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.71,0:10:08.04,Flashback,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I'll make you into a World Dai Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:11.11,Flashback,Kokona,0,0,0,,A World Dai Star...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:20.18,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(1088.936,399.075)\org(1092.921,376.155)\fscx100.292\fscy96.146\frz-4.376\frx-6.181\fax-0.027\fnImpact\xbord3.91\ybord3.75\c&H346A8E&\3c&H251C24&}Asakusa Hisago Street
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:20.18,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(1004.307,760.155)\fay0.05\fnArial\fs48\b1\c&H444641&\3c&HC7CFD2&}Asakusa Hisago Shopping Street
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:20.19,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,So I think Shizuka{**-chan}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:24.93,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,is a version of me that has \Neverything I've ever wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:29.70,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,A me who's good at acting, \Nsuper confident, and cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.84,0:10:33.85,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Though I'm too embarrassed \Nto tell Shizuka{**-chan} that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:35.52,Default,Clerk,0,0,0,,{\an8}Stop on by!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:41.69,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,{\i1}So a Sense that allows her to create \Nan ideal version of herself as an example?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.84,0:10:40.91,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,{\an8}Count me in! Got any recommendations?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.11,0:10:43.24,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,{\an8}Everything looks so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:45.06,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,{\an8}I wonder what everyone likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:48.95,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,{\i1}But then there'd be no need for \NShizuka to show up on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:48.73,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,{\an8}Maybe these?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.93,0:10:56.25,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I think I came from Kokona's \Ndesire to become a World Dai Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.22,0:11:00.04,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I don't know who I am exactly,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.63,0:11:04.67,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,but I want to help Kokona \Nachieve her dream. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.59,0:11:08.02,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,So why'd you show up on stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:10.53,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Because Kokona wanted the \Nplay to be a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.18,0:11:12.22,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.78,0:11:15.30,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I honestly shouldn't have done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.71,0:11:21.49,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Because I only exist to make sure\Nshe can hold her own onstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.96,0:11:25.42,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,So... I probably won't do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.90,0:11:27.58,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Well, that's a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:30.49,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,But I think I finally figured something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.49,0:11:33.09,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,When she was playing the prince \Nin {\i1}The Little Mermaid{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.09,0:11:37.23,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Koko{**-chan} must've been channeling that \Nrole through you, Oshizu{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:39.77,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:41.62,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:49.54,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,You really {\i1}can{\i0} wear the same costume\N just by imagining yourself in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:50.90,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Must be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.01,0:11:54.59,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,On to the next outfit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.59,0:11:56.13,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,But why?
