Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.49,0:12:13.51,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,And now, we're going to be making \Nthe home-style German dish
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.51,0:12:15.32,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,that Kathrina{**-chan} recommended...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.32,0:12:16.43,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Schuniterun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.43,0:12:17.92,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,It's {\i1}schnitzel{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:20.63,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Schnitzel! Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.63,0:12:26.51,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an9\pos(1785.231,664.152)\frz348.4\fnLato\fs30\b1\bord0\c&H93B28D&\fad(150,1)}Schnitzel\N\N{\fs24\b0\c&H5D5D5D&}Lean pork\NBlock of bacon\NPotatoes\NGreen beans\NCherry tomatoes\NLemon\NItalian parsley\NPanko
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.16,0:12:26.52,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,It's basically German tonkatsu, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.52,0:12:29.13,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Well... Sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.13,0:12:32.58,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Japanese tonkatsu is really good too, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:34.18,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,And deep-fried horse mackerel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.43,0:12:37.19,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, \NKathrina{**-chan}, the way you eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.62,0:12:40.19,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Are you getting any veggies?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.49,0:12:41.56,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,But of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:44.69,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Japanese vegetable juice is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:46.70,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(891.69,712.155)\frz349.4\fnArial\fs24\c&H385D36&\3c&HF3FDF8&\fad(270,480)}27 Delicious Daily Veg
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:48.74,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.92,0:12:51.43,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,How do we make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.59,0:12:53.46,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.43,0:13:01.08,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Season the meat and then coat it with flour.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:04.58,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Then quickly dip it in the egg...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:12.71,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,We're going to melt the butter first.\N Otherwise, these'll burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.71,0:13:14.47,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,So you're good at cooking?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.78,0:13:20.15,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I wouldn't say that, but both \Nof my parents always worked late,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.76,0:13:23.60,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,so I was in charge of making dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:36.22,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Okay, all set.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.85,0:13:41.22,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Could I ask you to handle the frying since \Nyou've actually had these before?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.22,0:13:42.16,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.37,0:13:43.18,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.73,0:13:44.97,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:47.79,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I'll prepare the side dishes in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.79,0:13:49.19,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:55.69,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,{\i1}I mean... I've studied\Nhow to play a chef before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:13:58.99,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is a stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.39,0:14:02.06,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm a chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:04.09,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm a chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.47,0:14:05.97,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm a chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:08.08,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm a chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:14.58,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(910.155,595.848)\frz14.6\fnTimes New Roman\fs108\b1\c&HF3F3F3&\3c&H333333&\4c&H333333&\fad(270,1)}A master chef is born!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.12,0:14:22.54,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Ooh, that already sounds delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.98,0:14:24.60,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Smells great, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.60,0:14:26.42,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Hmm? Is that smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:29.84,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:34.97,Default,Kathrina (Hamlet),0,0,0,,To be or not to be—that is the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:36.24,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hamlet{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.13,0:14:45.28,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I guess it's true that \Nno one is twice blessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:46.60,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.12,0:14:49.29,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,You actually suck \Nat everything besides acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.25,0:14:54.40,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,What?! I'm sure I would've \Nbeen fine if this were a play!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.40,0:14:55.68,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.17,0:14:58.03,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I think so... probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:15:02.14,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I see. So there are things \Neven you aren't good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.14,0:15:03.16,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Is that a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.77,0:15:04.99,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:09.67,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I'm just happy that I got \Nto learn more about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:13.81,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I didn't know anything about you\Nexcept that you're an amazing actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.04,0:15:19.35,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I'm not a good actress either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:21.66,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Even you must've been disappointed in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.66,0:15:22.31,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:27.56,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Everyone in my last troupe was.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.99,0:15:34.66,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I always performed alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:41.76,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I forced my costars and the staff to follow \Nthe ideal performance in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.70,0:15:47.33,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,The only reason they tolerated me is because \NI'm the daughter of World Dai Stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.99,0:15:48.93,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:03.79,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I ruined an important performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:10.37,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I was supposed to succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.06,0:16:14.80,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,For my costars, the audience...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.79,0:16:17.57,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,For my parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.67,0:16:23.91,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Yet I couldn't move. And now here again, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:26.98,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Say, why don't we go ahead and try again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.98,0:16:27.68,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:33.80,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I've messed up a bunch of times, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:36.38,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I failed a bunch of auditions,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:42.14,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Shizuka{**-chan} always yells at me, \Nand I lost the Princess Kaguya role.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.65,0:16:51.12,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,But I don't think I'll ever forget \Nyour performance as Princess Kaguya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.56,0:16:54.15,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Because it was our first play!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.23,0:16:58.94,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Next time we do {\i1}The Tale of the Bamboo Cutter{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.94,0:17:03.66,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,let's both do our best \Nand get even more applause!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.78,0:17:06.66,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Kokona.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:10.93,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I'll do this, too! Teach me how!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.75,0:17:13.68,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.79,0:17:17.48,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,And... thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.92,0:17:19.63,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.29,0:17:26.90,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Okay! Is everyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:28.35,Default,Kokona; Shizuka; Sasuga,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:33.86,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Hiiragi{**-san}... What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:35.37,Default,Shamo,0,0,0,,Don't worry about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:39.59,Default,Shamo,0,0,0,,She's just relieved now \Nthat the play is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.59,0:17:43.14,Default,Shamo,0,0,0,,She had a lot of stress pent up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:48.87,Default,Shamo,0,0,0,,She was apparently sleeping \Nall day in her room, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:51.89,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,It's like night and day...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.89,0:17:53.34,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Uh, why are you two so close?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.02,0:17:55.23,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Look who's talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.23,0:17:57.34,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Well, I'm Kokona's Sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.52,0:18:01.14,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Why are you two so eager to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.88,0:18:04.64,Default,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:06.41,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\move(939.693,649.386,939.693,1169.31)\frz351.5\fnArial\fs36\b1\bord0\c&H0D3733&}Taiyaki
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.91,0:18:06.05,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yae{**-chan}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.05,0:18:06.96,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,{\an8}What gives?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:09.36,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,We invited her as a surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:11.48,Default,Niizuma,0,0,0,,They were kind enough to include me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:14.62,Default,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Also, I brought some taiyaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.52,0:18:16.81,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,What an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.81,0:18:19.13,Default,Kokona and Shizuka,0,0,0,,Come sit over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:20.25,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.17,0:18:22.80,Default,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.55,0:18:29.93,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Okay! Now we can officially \Nwelcome you to Sirius Sento!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.93,0:18:31.08,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.36,0:18:33.32,Default,All but Kathrina and Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:40.34,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an7\move(1545.693,498.921,1715.541,498.921)\frz110.4\fnTimes New Roman\fs48\b1\bord0\c&H191A33&}The\NStar\Nof\NAsakusa
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.65,0:18:50.62,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,My mouth is full of Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.07,0:18:52.45,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.14,0:18:56.79,Default,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Is this a dish from your \Nhomeland, Kathrina{**-san}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.79,0:19:00.98,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Yes... Though Kokona made most of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.98,0:19:04.32,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,But you got a lot better at it,\N Kathrina{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:11.53,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Koko{**-chan} and Kathrin seem \Nto be getting along great!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.45,0:19:16.29,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Well, they are roommates,\Nso that's probably for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.29,0:19:17.80,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,But how do you really feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.19,0:19:20.90,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I hate it! I feel like she's \Ntaking Kokona from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.90,0:19:22.22,Default,Panda and Sasuga,0,0,0,,Ooh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:24.70,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Don't make me admit that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:27.05,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Are you good at cooking too, Yae{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:30.72,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Why did the newbies cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.72,0:19:31.77,Default,All,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:33.80,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,You mean it's not a dorm tradition?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.62,0:19:36.56,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,First I've heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:41.64,Default,Sasuga (Impersonating Panda),0,0,0,,"Let's give Kathrin an opportunity \Nto apologize to Koko{**-chan}!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.64,0:19:44.05,Default,Sasuga (Impersonating Panda),0,0,0,,"Her being so pouty is honestly a pain."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:45.93,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,That's what Panda said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:48.17,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Heh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:50.16,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:51.43,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Oho...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.15,0:19:54.14,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I-I wasn't being pouty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.14,0:19:56.17,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Who asked for your help anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:59.29,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,What? I did you a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.20,0:20:04.45,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,I'm sure you're thinking, "Thank you, \NPanda{**-chan}! You're super adorable!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:07.06,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,That's what your \Nheart of hearts is saying, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.06,0:20:08.77,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,No, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:10.60,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Oh, come on now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.01,0:20:15.20,Default,Shamo,0,0,0,,Some rather interesting girls \Nhave joined the troupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.20,0:20:18.06,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Yes. I think I'm finally starting to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.71,0:20:25.57,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Panda, Chisa, Yae, Kathrina, \NKokona, and Shizuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:30.72,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,I'm sure something will be born \Nonce their Senses collide.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.91,0:20:37.64,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,I'll do my best to nurture them...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:42.71,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,into World Dai Stars representing SIRIUS \Nand following in your footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.92,0:20:44.92,Default,Shamo,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:57.76,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,North! Let's go north!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:05.03,Subtitles,Sign,0,0,0,,Will you be okay all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:13.57,Subtitles,Sign,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.57,0:21:15.82,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't worry, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.16,0:21:21.70,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,No, Kathrina{**-chan}... Don't go that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.40,0:21:26.86,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not alone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.18,0:21:30.57,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,North, north...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.12,0:21:40.89,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,All right, so that will be our next play.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.27,0:21:44.36,Default,Kudo,0,0,0,,Yae{**-chan}'s starring again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.39,0:21:46.71,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.15,0:21:52.21,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.11,0:21:56.39,Default,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.35,0:21:59.49,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.93,0:22:04.32,Default,Niizuma,0,0,0,,I have a request regarding our next show.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.02,0:23:40.02,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(952.401,307.599)\fnTimes New Roman\fs60\bord3\3c&H4B4B4C&\blur6}Fifth Stage
